## Model Routing

This project uses the Istishraf plugin with `opusplan`.

| Phase | Model | How to activate |
|---|---|---|
| Strategic thinking (Phases 0–2, `/strategize`, `/think-deeper`, `/premortem`) | Opus | Press **Shift+Tab** to enter plan mode |
| Implementation & review (Phases 3–5, `/implement`, `/review`) | Sonnet | Press **Shift+Tab** to exit plan mode |

Standard session flow:
```
[Shift+Tab] → /istishraf <ticket or problem> → Foresight Report approved → [Shift+Tab] → implementation
```

