### Jira workflow (if using Jira MCP)

When a Jira ticket ID is provided to `/istishraf` or `/implement`:
1. Fetch the full ticket via the Jira MCP tool
2. Extract acceptance criteria and map them to the Foresight Report's success criteria
3. Reference the ticket ID in every commit message
4. Transition ticket status: `To Do` → `In Progress` (Phase 3 start) → `In Review` (PR opened)
5. Add a comment to the ticket when the PR is opened

